<title>USA: Harris &amp; Harris writes down investments.</title>
<headline>Harris &amp; Harris writes down investments.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Harris &amp; Harris Group Inc said on Friday it had written down its investment in two private portfolio companies, PureSpeech Inc and Harber Brothers Productions Inc.</p>
<p>Harris &amp; Harris Group has written down its investment in PureSpeech from $999,999 to $166,667 and its investment in Harber Brothers from $1,217,500 to one dollar.</p>
<p>On an after-tax basis, these write-downs will reduce Harris &amp; Harris Group's net assets by approximately $1.3 million, the company said.</p>
